    {
      "id": "61c07fa5aff09e000032efb9",
      "text": "なぜ足場を捨て去ることに抵抗があるか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640005541,
      "updated": 1640005554
    },
    {
      "id": "61c07fb2aff09e000032efba",
      "text": "　それは「まとめ」に書いた以上の情報がまだ残っているから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640005554,
      "updated": 1640005571
    },
    {
      "id": "61c07fc3aff09e000032efbb",
      "text": "　それを出し切ってしまえばよい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640005572,
      "updated": 1640005586
    },
    {
      "id": "61c07fd2aff09e000032efbc",
      "text": "　(もちろん将来的には出し切らなくても保存しておいて、後で必要になった時にまた取り出して使えるのが理想)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640005586,
      "updated": 1640005627
    },
    {
      "id": "61c07ffaaff09e000032efbd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640005627,
      "updated": 1640005639
    },
    {
      "id": "61c08af9aff09e0000b03fb3",
      "text": "[華厳まとめ]は「理解の検証のために自分の言葉でまとめ」たもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640008441,
      "updated": 1640008472
    },
    {
      "id": "61c08b18aff09e000032efd4",
      "text": "　その結果、自分の言葉とオリジナルのキーワードとの間のリンクが失われている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640008472,
      "updated": 1640008491
    },
    {
      "id": "61c08b2caff09e000032efd5",
      "text": "　オリジナルのキーワードを活かしたまとめが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640008493,
      "updated": 1640008506
    },
    {
      "id": "61c0828eaff09e000032efc0",
      "text": "\t[華厳Kozanebaまとめ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640006286,
      "updated": 1640008529
    },
    {
      "id": "61c08b52aff09e0000b03fb4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640008530,
      "updated": 1640008530
    },
    {
      "id": "61c08cecaff09e000032efd6",
      "text": "ここまでまとめたら納得した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640008940,
      "updated": 1640008946
    },
    {
      "id": "61c08cf1aff09e000032efd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1640008946,
      "updated": 1640008946
    },
    {
